articles.title: Sister Princess Re Pure - Episode 10 - The Red String of Fate
articles.description: Big Brother gets a love letter! Sakuya decides to stick close and protect him from his other admirers, but can she confess her own feelings? Afterwards, Marie has a sweet dream of her brother.

articles.title: Sister Princess Re Pure - Episode 9 - You're Right Next to Me, Aren't You, Bro?
articles.description: Rinrin and Yotsuba get curious about what Big Brother does when he's out alone, and decide to follow him secretly around town. Afterwards, Haruka thinks about her first Tanabata festival together with Big Brother.

articles.title: Sister Princess Re Pure - Episode 7 - Magic Words
articles.description: Aria spends a day with Big Brother, but she's sad when it ends... so she hatches a plan to make him come back! Afterwards, Chikage prepares a sinister ritual to win Big Brother's love for herself alone.

articles.title: Sister Princess Re Pure - Episode 6 - Mugs for Big Bro and Me
articles.description: Big Brother and the sisters go on a camping trip. Mamoru had a gift for Big Brother, but will she get the chance to give it to him? Afterwards, Rin Rin remembers how her grandpa taught her to love inventing things.

articles.title: Sister Princess Re Pure - Episode 5 - Inexhaustible Wishes on a Shooting Star
articles.description: A strange girl who looks like Chikage gives Big Brother a ticket to the planetarium... then, later, demands it back! It's not easy, but Big Brother solves the mystery. Afterwards, Kaho remembers the pretty red shoes she got long ago.

articles.title: Sister Princess Re Pure - Episode 1 - Heart Days
articles.description: Karen and the eleven other sisters are is excited to meet their beloved big brother again! They bustle about town to get ready for his arrival, and mishaps befall them as they do, but Big Brother's understanding knows no bounds.

articles.title: Sister Princess Re Pure - Episode 2 - The Secret Garden!
articles.description: Kaho prepares a special gift for Big Brother, but it goes missing! Luckily her sister, girl detective Yotsuba, is determined to solve the case. Afterwards, Mamoru remembers how she struggled with her tomboyish nature until Big Brother helped.

articles.title: Sister Princess Re Pure - Episode 12 - Dear Brother's Restaurant
articles.description: Thanks to Sakuya's hard work, the sisters go to a fancy restaurant with Big Brother and have a lovely evening. Afterwards, Sakuya dreams of being Big Brother's bride and getting married in a church.

articles.title: Sister Princess Re Pure - Episode 3 - Chestnut Temptation
articles.description: Kaho weighs herself, and the results are devastating! She goes on a diet, but it's hard for her as Big Bro and her sisters enjoy sweets together. Afterwards, Aria finds herself in a mysterious, magical mansion...

articles.title: Sister Princess Re Pure - Episode 11 - Treasure Chest of Memories
articles.description: Sakuya is heartbroken when Big Brother doesn't recognize the gift he once gave her. She runs away and wanders the town, awakening her own memories of her time with Big Brother. Afterwards, Shirayuki reminisces about how she learned to bake and make sweets.

articles.title: Sister Princess Re Pure - Episode 8 - Visiting Day!
articles.description: Big Brother spends the day with Maria, while Karen tries to keep Aria and Hinako occupied to give them some time alone. Afterwards, Yotsuba remembers the time when she first moved from England and met her brother.

articles.title: Sister Princess Re Pure - Episode 4 - Staying Over
articles.description: Kaho's staying over at Big Brother's place, and she buys cute new pajamas with her sisters' help. They have a fun-filled evening together. Afterwards, Hinako goes out in the rain and faces her fiercest enemy yet: a frog!

articles.title: Sister Princess Re Pure - Episode 13 - Pure Christmas
articles.description: Big Brother and the sisters get ready for a special Christmas together, but none of them can decide on which present to get for their brother until they have a brilliant idea. Then Big Brother works hard to make sure the Christmas tree is perfect!
